:

1. *Radiš* svoj posao. (You are doing your job.)
2. Ona *radiše* puno sati. (She worked for many hours.)
3. Oni su *radili* kao ludi. (They were working like crazy.)
4. Njegov sin *radi* u beogradskoj bolnici. (His son works in a hospital in Belgrade.)
5. Mi ćemo *raditi* zajedno. (We will work together.)
6. Oni su *radili* sve što su mogli. (They did all they could.)
7. Ja *radim* svoj posao dobro. (I am doing my job well.)
8. Da li znaš da on *radi* za to preduzeće? (Do you know that he works for that company?)
9. Ona je *radila* dobro svoj posao. (She did her job well.)
10. *Radiš* li ti ovde? (Are you working here?)